column2: Dogness (International) Corp. engages in the design and manufacture of pet products, including leashes and smart products. The company is headquartered in Dongguan, Guangdong and currently employs 288 full-time employees. The firm is engaged in designing and manufacturing of pet products in the Peopleâ€™s Republic of China. The firm offers range of products such as C2 smart collar, H2 smart harness, nylon and leather collar, anti shock leash, and neoprene and nylon harness. The firm has designed its smart collars to allow owners to find their dogs easily, where the dogs are and to communicate with their pets from around the world. The firm also built communication model around SIM cards and provides cellular data service for the collars.
